---
// Placeholder demo block — user will drop in a video URL or live embed later.
---

<section id="demo" class="section-pad relative">
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0"
    style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 50% 50%, rgba(168,0,42,0.12), transparent);"
  ></div>

  <div class="container-x relative">
    <div class="reveal mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <div class="section-eyebrow justify-center">
        <span class="h-px w-8 bg-hac-red-light"></span>
        Live Demo
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title">
        See it <span class="text-gradient-hot">in action</span>.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-300">
        A short walkthrough of UNI-CHAT answering a real student question with
        full source attribution.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Video frame placeholder -->
    <div class="reveal mt-14 mx-auto max-w-5xl">
      <div class="group relative aspect-video overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-ink-900 shadow-2xl shadow-hac-red/10">
        <!-- Pattern -->
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 opacity-30"
          style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 40px 40px;"
        ></div>

        <!-- Glow -->
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -left-20 -top-20 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-accent-magenta/20 blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-20 -right-20 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-accent-cyan/20 blur-3xl"></div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="relative flex h-full flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6 p-8 text-center">
          <div class="grid h-20 w-20 place-items-center rounded-full bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md ring-1 ring-white/20 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110">
            <svg class="h-9 w-9 translate-x-0.5 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent-cyan">
              Demo video coming soon
            </div>
            <div class="mt-2 font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white">
              We'll embed the walkthrough here
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Fake terminal preview -->
          <div class="mt-2 w-full max-w-xl rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-ink-950/60 p-4 text-left font-mono text-xs">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 pb-3">
              <span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-accent-magenta/60"></span>
              <span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-accent-amber/60"></span>
              <span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-accent-violet/60"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-slate-400">$ <span class="text-white">unichat ask</span> "Staj kaç gün?"</div>
            <div class="mt-2 text-accent-cyan">▸ retrieving (hybrid mode)...</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-accent-magenta">▸ resolving norm hierarchy: L1 &gt; L2 &gt; L3</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-accent-violet">▸ 3 sources cited</div>
            <div class="mt-3 text-slate-200">
              Bilgisayar Mühendisliği bölümü için zorunlu staj süresi <span class="text-white">30 iş günüdür</span>.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
